public abstract class AbstractNullStringValidator
extends Object
implements org.databene.commons.Validator<String>

Parent class for AludraTest text validations: If the validation term is null, empty or equal to DataConfiguration.NULL_MARKER, it accepts any string. Otherwise it examines the text to validate and, if null then returns false, otherwise forwards to the validImpl(String) method to be implemented by child classes.

Author:
Volker Bergmann
